com.aliyun.oss.crypto

类 RenewableCipherInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class RenewableCipherInputStream
extends CipherInputStream
    A specific kind of CipherInputStream that supports partial mark-and-reset in the sense that, if the underlying input stream supports mark-and-reset, this input stream can then be marked at and get reset back to the very beginning of the stream (but not anywhere else).
